Defect Reporting is the process of identifying, documenting, and reporting defects found during testing. 
Defect reporting is documenting and reporting defects found during testing. 
A report should include essential information to help developers reproduce and fix the issue.
ex:
 Defect ID                                lct-001        
 Title                                 login button is not working
 Description                           details description
 Severity/Priority                      high,low
  Steps to Reproduce                    step by step instruction
  Expected and Actual Results            expected vs actual result behaviour
  Environment                             os , browser
 Attachments                             (screenshots, videos, etc.)

